Yum!  Yum!  Yum!  Perfect Mexican food in Barcelona. If you like American west coast Mexican and are tired of tapas, eat here!  My husband said its the "best" Mexican food he's had all year!!!!  We started with two limon margaritas and the nachos with cheese. Delicious!  The Hubbs had the hot pot of shredded pork with red onions and I had the carnitas tacos. Truly delicious!
